<h1>Announcing Tribal Fan</h1>
<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lawfwu0Zmn1qzbc4f.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>I think we might have it. We might have our big idea! It was born last
night. It’s called Tribal Fan. It’s sort of like a sports’ social
network. This idea is going to <a href="http://techneur.com/post/935550443/the-startup-idea-filter">marinate for
awhile</a>.
But, it seems to bring together everything that I felt was lacking
on game days, forums, etc. Ideally, we would deploy this in the summer,
right before the Huskers move to the Big 10.</p>
<p>As it progresses, I’ll announce more.</p>
